  "name": "RPlog_Templars_Allies_versus_Pirates_-_Part_2",
  "title": "Boarding the Pirate Hulk",
  "summary": "With the pirate fighters destroyed, Colonel Eckhart leads his marines and allies aboard the abandoned pirate base, a derelict mining rig cobbled together from scavenged ships and reeking of death. As Druze untangles the rig's sensor data and Siarra's EOD team disarms booby traps along corroded catwalks, the boarders discover the aftermath of a mutiny: piles of dead bodies, ransacked rooms, and one dying Zeltron pirate found by Cort who gasps out that the crew mutinied and abandoned ship. Tiaryn and Eckhart track faint cries to a locked room and free a caged, starving Loth-cat and her newborn kittens, while Kelnas and Samyok hit a jackpot of looted medical supplies, weapons, fuel cells, and credits, and Siarra finds evidence the pirates trafficked slaves. The reverie shatters when a cryoban grenade rolls from beneath the now-dead Zeltron, its countdown ticking down, and the team grabs what they can, rescues the cats, and races back to the shuttle, jumping to hyperspace just as the pirate base erupts in a blinding explosion.",
